{"tid":1978260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（睇唔過眼）呃口罩錢 NOPER.HK","createTime":"2020-04-18T14:33:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T18:22:30.000Z","uid":162491,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a82275dae293fe25fcc1507ef52bf8ee984672bc","tid":1978260,"uid":162491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:33:36.000Z","msg":"我有朋友係ig shop買口罩中左伏<br />\n佢比啲對話我睇 我都睇唔過眼要po上黎<br />\n是咁的，<a href=\"http://佢一月個陣跟左間叫noper.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E4%BD%A2%E4%B8%80%E6%9C%88%E5%80%8B%E9%99%A3%E8%B7%9F%E5%B7%A6%E9%96%93%E5%8F%ABnoper.hk&d=TvWZhBC8jRU6oyAzZT7RDoVlFhl8e2VpHQ9vpRm7Uxg%3D&h=7761c12a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">佢一月個陣跟左間叫noper.hk</a>訂口罩<br />\n個時講到係美國船運返黎 所以就跟左佢訂<br />\n但點知隔左一排見佢無乜聲氣就見到以下呢個story<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/khftjXm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkhftjXm.jpg&h=0f9e230b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如是者見到佢有交代 就冇再特別問佢<br />\n直到有一日屎忽痕就走去問佢啲口罩既情況如何<br />\n然後就有以下既回應<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wQhfKqe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwQhfKqe.jpg&h=81b6803a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AHg0VwV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAHg0VwV.jpg&h=a9a78c50&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AKRka5g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAKRka5g.jpg&h=f0541ac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5w8ZrD2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5w8ZrD2.jpg&h=83527229&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kN7jrD3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkN7jrD3.jpg&h=797adf00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uFgka5K.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuFgka5K.jpg&h=27518715&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PN5tjY5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPN5tjY5.jpg&h=22b6bcb6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9Bd28Sr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9Bd28Sr.jpg&h=0833a7f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P5Qhdjt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP5Qhdjt.jpg&h=1c71703d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nOSGEZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnOSGEZu.jpg&h=47cc3687&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bFpFa6a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbFpFa6a.jpg&h=409d9541&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5HPqncR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5HPqncR.jpg&h=235176e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後附送一個彩蛋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不眠不休on duty左三個月嘅店長辛苦晒<br />\n真係好盡責，一問你新貨就即刻覆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NQ3R2de.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNQ3R2de.jpg&h=bd67543e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a71e6ebe598067fad9e6aa97804a4a762482785c","tid":1978260,"uid":86452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:36:33.000Z","msg":"嘩 我睇完都好嬲 明明自己錯郁咁既態度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca59a8d54c46152eb3b34184a49ad78d5b6b41b7","tid":1978260,"uid":54126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-18T14:37:12.000Z","msg":"你自爆左<br />\ntina yuen<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cdfd2d2ae05525e426c7c559fd2f9ff91e37c95","tid":1978260,"uid":162491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"s